<section class="faq-section"><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="faq-list"><div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How do I fill the urn pendant?</div><div class="faq-a">Each necklace includes an easy-to-use filling kit with step-by-step instructions and a small pin to help guide ashes into the chamber.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What birthstones are available?</div><div class="faq-a">We offer all 12 monthly birthstones: Garnet, Amethyst, Aquamarine, Diamond, Emerald, Alexandrite, Ruby, Peridot, Sapphire, Opal, Topaz, and Tanzanite.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Is the necklace waterproof?</div><div class="faq-a">Yes! The cylinder is sealed with a threaded, screw-top cap that is water-resistant for daily wear. We recommend removing before swimming or showering for maximum longevity.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How long is the chain?</div><div class="faq-a">The premium stainless steel chain is 18 inches (45 cm) with a 2-inch extender, allowing you to adjust the length for perfect positioning.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Can this hold human ashes too?</div><div class="faq-a">Yes, this urn necklace can hold a small portion of human or pet ashes. Many customers use it to honor both beloved pets and family members.</div></div><div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What is your return policy?</div><div class="faq-a">We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. If you&#39;re not completely happy, contact us for a full refund or exchange.</div></div></div></section>